OL,5, Top oil executives have appeared before
OL,6, US lawmakers to face allegations they  
OL,7, misled the public about climate change.
OL,9,FMajor producers were quizzed about the 
OL,10,Fimpact of the fossil fuels they profit 
OL,11,Ffrom on their effects on the climate.  
OL,13,FDemocrat lawmakers described the       
OL,14,Fhearings as "historic" and hope they   
OL,15,Fwill help shift public view like with  
OL,16,Fthe tobacco industry in the 1990s.     
OL,18,FThe hearings, involving firms like BP  
OL,19,Fand Shell, come days before the start  
OL,20,Fof the UN's COP26 climate conference.  
